comments.raw_text: I've marked the failing test as 'todo'. The issue is that we read the 'currentTime' when the video is paused, but this time can vary depending on the data held in the sound buffers. Because it varies it is prone to intermittent failures.
comments.text:
Created attachment 555926
Mark test as 'todo'

I've marked the failing test as 'todo'. The issue is that we read the 'currentTime' when the video is paused, but this time can vary depending on the data held in the sound buffers. Because it varies it is prone to intermittent failures.
